# Privacy Policy for Neon Dash

**Last updated: January 2026**

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Neon Dash ("Application") for mobile devices that was created by Tyler Rudd. The Application is a game that displays advertisements.

## Information We Collect

The Application does not create any user accounts, nor does it collect specific personal information like your name, address, or phone number.

However, the Application uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you (Advertising ID) to serve personalized ads.

### Third-Party Services
The Application uses the following third-party services:
* **AdMob (Google):** We use AdMob to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and use your device's Advertising ID to serve personalized ads based on your interests.
    * [Link to AdMob Privacy Policy](https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543?hl=en)

## Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.

## Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at: [YOUR_EMAIL_HERE]
